unittitle_ssm: Adrian Martense and Jacobus Van Duyne bond of indenture and related documents
abstract_ssm: This collection consists of a circa 1780-1800 bond of indenture between Adrian Martense and Jacobus Van Duyne, both of the town of Flatbush in Kings County, as well as two financial documents relating to the bond.
